 171	2. Expected: Each gets current time stamp
 172	3. Result: All students marked with same time
 173	
 174	### **Technical Notes**
 175	
 176	#### **Time Source**:
 177	- **Browser Local Time**: Uses client-side time
 178	- **Format**: JavaScript Date.toTimeString().slice(0, 5)
 179	- **Timezone**: Follows user's system timezone
 180	
 181	#### **Performance**:
 182	- **Lightweight**: Minimal computational overhead
 183	- **Instant**: No network calls required
